@Node "PREQ_NewRequester()" "palette.requester/PREQ_NewRequester"

@{b}   NAME@{ub}
       PREQ_NewRequester -- @{"Allocate" Link "exec/Allocate()"} a new Palette requester.

@{b}   SYNOPSIS@{ub}
       Object = PREQ_NewRequester(Tags,...)

       Object *PREQ_NewRequester(Tag, ...);
       a0                        a0

       Object *PREQ_NewRequesterA(struct TagItem *)
       a0                                a0

@{b}   FUNCTION@{ub}
       Allocates a new Palette requester object.
       The palette requester is a BOOPSI object.
       Further settings can be changed or read
       with SetAttrs() or @{"GetAttr()" Link "intuition/GetAttr()"}.


